The paper discusses a mechanism design approach for sponsored search, which involves auctions and resource allocation. This falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes a new auction mechanism, which involves efficient distribution of resources, making it relevant to distributed systems (cs.DS), electronic commerce (cs.EC), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
